<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//ae1c/ae1c139145aa001f5d54d2694e0fe289.com/large/1922000529a5af38e097"></p> 
<p>这是我之前在乡下干活打的煮面的灶，今天准备吃个小火锅，为了好用需要把灶改造一下。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//3f79/3f7916386c86d18ff1a60741bbaefae4.com/large/192700051426df0943e4"></p> 
<p>主要改造烟囱，向上顺着原来的烟囱挖一条沟，然后用石头架空用湿泥巴堵缝。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//97d1/97d1fa7443ddac363c7a6f45e0246674.com/large/192500050e1ba5d7f2fa"></p> 
<p>改造完成，目的是增大抽风量和让烟远离火锅灶。这样吃火锅的时候不会被烟呛也不会烤手。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//75d3/75d3cfb427fb9763885dcc38dce20984.com/large/1922000529d98c95d599"></p> 
<p>烟就从后面跑出去了，并且烟也很小。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//d4e5/d4e59451f2502c5ad71e952f26279cc3.com/large/192500050e54f78a1dbb"></p> 
<p>火会烧的很旺，自然进风，不需要吹，不需要端锅灶门加柴火力好控制。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//c736/c736ef72834164a6c7e1837f7ea8e5d4.com/large/192400051afe4a888012"></p> 
<p>我们今天3个人，朋友自己又打了个新灶。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//ba54/ba54e5dcd949f1e2893802bbbb06b0d2.com/large/191d0006f31c9944d496"></p> 
<p>打如果烟囱挖小了就这样，不但烟大还不扯火，烟囱扩大后正常。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//7108/7108d63c2b750aff9e92995d591a10bf.com/large/192300051de8183a2dff"></p> 
<p>这是我们的锅，下面是今天的小菜。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//80f1/80f11e8dbb2044f26e377fa8cb67d869.com/large/192500050f0517e2de0b"></p> 
<p>主食大米</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//b5d3/b5d3faa76cafb99bc2344149d747e6c5.com/large/192200052aa91826563d"></p> 
<p>大白萝卜(路过时问山里大叔要的)</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//0ade/0ade254d75516e785d95ea39b2ee8189.com/large/1927000515141267d40d"></p> 
<p>火锅底料<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//e337/e33788a316e358f02c594d6fbb24a20b.com/large/191d0006f3825b39802e"></p> 
<p>也是要的<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//553b/553b4a0dd498c5935a7ca08c302626eb.com/large/191d0006f385fb1580c6"></p> 
<p>火锅粉皮<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//f00f/f00f73f64769984efda10f919946bce2.com/large/19270005151a493c81f4"></p> 
<p>豆腐皮</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//d64b/d64b7cff2e87eb3ffa320b2dd86ba149.com/large/191d0006f38d1f29269a"></p> 
<p>红薯粉条</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//c330/c330ec095eaa9dcc12ce68b2e7c025e9.com/large/192500050f18064e7dbd"></p> 
<p>朋友送的青岗木耳</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//bfdb/bfdbf1c811d4ef2bfa44add0b4eab057.com/large/191d0006f38f42d2699b"></p> 
<p>土豆粉</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//a713/a7136232a835e60894ab28b2464de209.com/large/192300051e4db9f833e7"></p> 
<p>魔芋粉皮</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//ffd5/ffd52fe663ef41b927da74a1ffa25e0a.com/large/192200052ac3947bc967"></p> 
<p>香芋粉</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//c721/c721fcf17a54b1a89bebb80c969b0aa4.com/large/192700051526ace9b423"></p> 
<p>酸菜豆腐</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//a97c/a97c23a9d3b56536fbb7ff85578ff99d.com/large/192200052acb06f6497e"></p> 
<p>青冈木香菇</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//a404/a4048f9d4f6044d3f025449c454e3c71.com/large/192400051bd0a1b1046b"></p> 
<p>2瓶二锅头</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//a7c8/a7c8200c756d73a8f019c6e60fee79a0.com/large/191d0006f3a7e58cc5f9"></p> 
<p>在这地方接的水</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//d8be/d8be9c96b50403238b3688da6cc1f336.com/large/192200052acd032762c4"></p> 
<p>水桶<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//9f78/9f789a4dd88a6442683ce3632ff3c83f.com/large/192500050f31396b8b54"></p> 
<p>柴刀（必备）</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//f7de/f7dea15114ad96037805eed9db1991f4.com/large/192200052ad47642e730"></p> 
<p>捡柴<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//be67/be67d990c5701b9e45dad0168e00f7a9.com/large/192400051bdbc0ab5b43"></p> 
<p>下面准备做米饭</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//d3b4/d3b4903922f1618cf009af772e702685.com/large/192200052b0e6cd06299"></p> 
<p>放入大米洗干净</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//c0d0/c0d0d939a6d3ebbc2948ae2d4eb6b763.com/large/19270005156623a51dab"></p> 
<p>加足够多的水（没把握的尽量多加，因为下来还要把多余的水滤出来，不用担心水过量）放在灶上煮。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//19d8/19d8ae042d4acb8f41d528973c8aea00.com/large/192200052b10454f1942"></p> 
<p>这是重点：煮到米只有一点白心时(大概剩下1.5毫米的白硬心),这时候把水全部沥掉，铺均匀用筷子扎几个眼</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//e0f1/e0f1f3c7dd29ca22655ac6f47f18cb40.com/large/191d0006f3e9b9ad4a34"></p> 
<p>然后加盖放在灶上，撤掉明火（撤掉燃烧的柴火，只留炭火）</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//7abc/7abcf2ae00e5b236ceabbe883f379ca9.com/large/192200052b167b6f3188"></p> 
<p>把炭火铺平，看表15分钟。。。。。。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//592d/592d85257561cc215ba1112f542be0f4.com/large/192200052b18a6391a8f"></p> 
<p>15分钟后米饭就做好了（想吃锅巴的加长时间，或适当加大火力）</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//30a5/30a573dfbcd42087ab2d86fa8785d1f6.com/large/192200053a961007b1c1"></p> 
<p>加水放入火锅底料(也可以放入食用油，葱，蒜，姜，再把火锅料炒一下味道更好）</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//509a/509a3efd613e25d5901aa65d638b5ef9.com/large/192300051ec6335f84a4"></p> 
<p>加入小菜</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//e4d3/e4d37cea5ec4df5f1a16650b07fcc22c.com/large/192500050f77fc94575d"></p> 
<p>米饭就火锅，味道还不错</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//2004/20049c7efec24c917d5f0c042e8c7238.com/large/192700051580e43e015c"></p> 
<p>配两瓶二锅头，保证浑身冒汗。。。。。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//dcd4/dcd47e598c2425093e987a9f3aec678b.com/large/192700051589f6458d31"></p> 
<p>又麻又辣</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//05dc/05dcf74657b907d1d394588152e34de6.com/large/192400051c39241ee339"></p> 
<p>吃完收工，灭火，收拾垃圾。</p> 
